# The source UNHCR guideline PDFs (RAG provenance) are NOT in git — the HF Hub
# rejects binary files in plain git (must use Xet/LFS). They're uploaded to the
# Space directly via `hf upload` (auto-Xet); see deploy/DEPLOY.md.

